对  所以他愿意给三十五万元花红

842
00:56:02,530 --> 00:56:04,240
350? That's ridiculous!
三十五万？真是荒谬

843
00:56:04,320 --> 00:56:07,000
I'm really pushing out the boat for you, mate.
我已经为你尽力争取

844
00:56:07,080 --> 00:56:10,360
I'm busting my balls here. I made us the top house in SIMEX.
我很努力工作

845
00:56:10,440 --> 00:56:13,440
We even got that award for all the business we're doing!
我是市场最出色经纪  还因此得到奖项

846
00:56:13,520 --> 00:56:15,830
Yeah, I know that, Nick.
这点我知

847
00:56:15,920 --> 00:56:17,910
Look, I'll see what I can do.
我尽力吧

848
00:56:18,000 --> 00:56:20,760
I'll see if it can't start with a four, eh?
看我能够争取四十万

849
00:56:22,880 --> 00:56:24,790
That was their opening offer.
看我能够争取四十万

850
00:56:24,880 --> 00:56:28,960
He'd have thought something was wrong if I'd accepted it straight away.
若以为我会接受        便错了

851
00:56:29,040 --> 00:56:31,320
Yeah, it's like winning the lottery.
对，像中六合彩嘛

852
00:56:31,400 --> 00:56:33,390
They must think the world of you.
他们应答谢你呢

853
00:56:39,080 --> 00:56:41,200
What's the matter, Lisa?
丽莎，怎么了

854
00:56:41,280 --> 00:56:44,000
What do you think's the bloody matter, Nick?
尼克，你以为什么

855
00:56:44,080 --> 00:56:46,070
Everything's changed!
一切都改变了

856
00:56:46,960 --> 00:56:50,240
I just wanna go home. Get the hell out of here and go home.
我想回家，想离开这里

857
00:56:50,320 --> 00:56:53,390
But... you wanted to come back. What about the bonus?
你想回来，还说为花红

858
00:56:53,480 --> 00:56:56,230
Well, can't you get the bonus in London?
在伦敦拿到花红吗

859
00:56:56,320 --> 00:56:58,790
Please, Nick! I wanna get on with my life.
尼克，我想重头开始

860
00:56:58,880 --> 00:57:02,390
I wanna start a family. I'm going stir-crazy here all on my own!
建立家庭  离开这令人疯癫的地方

861
00:57:02,480 --> 00:57:07,630
Calm down. Look, I just need a bit more time to sort things out, turn things around.
好吧，冷静点，慢慢来...

862
00:57:07,720 --> 00:57:12,310
No! You're up at dawn and then you come back at night and collapse into bed...
你早出晚归，回来时倦极了

863
00:57:12,400 --> 00:57:15,710
How am I meant to get pregnant again if we never make love?
我们不干怎再次怀孕

864
00:57:15,800 --> 00:57:18,710
I know. But this could set us up for life!
我知，会影响我们生活

865
00:57:19,840 --> 00:57:24,510
- When's bonus day? - 24th of February. Just five weeks to go.
何时取得花红？          二月二十四，还有五周

866
00:57:24,600 --> 00:57:27,160
Right, we're gonna leave on the 25th.
好吧，我们二十五号离开

867
00:57:27,240 --> 00:57:30,510
I mean it. I'm calling the furniture removers tomorrow.
我叫搬运公司来收拾

868
00:57:30,600 --> 00:57:32,590
All right.
好吧

869
00:57:33,440 --> 00:57:35,430
All right.
好吧

870
00:57:36,280 --> 00:57:40,550
With everything else closing in on me, I'd forgotten about the mooning charge.
无论任何事我要熬下去

871
00:57:40,630 --> 00:57:44,020
When it finally came up, I was facing a possible jail sentence.
因为上到法庭我可能要坐牢

872
00:57:51,350 --> 00:57:54,110
The charge has been reduced to a misdemeanour.
控罪减为行为不检

873
00:57:54,190 --> 00:57:58,350
The maximum penalty is a $200 fine. I think we should plead guilty.
最高罚款是二百元        我们应该认罪

874
00:57:58,430 --> 00:58:00,390
Thank you very much.
谢谢你    谢谢

875
00:58:00,470 --> 00:58:03,310
It was uncanny. I'd got away with it again!
真够运，又再逃过大难

876
00:58:03,390 --> 00:58:07,910
To the Singapore legal system, a shining example to the free world!
为新加皮司法干杯       为自由世界干杯

877
00:58:07,990 --> 00:58:10,590
We bared our all for Barings.
为霸菱而喝采

878
00:58:10,670 --> 00:58:13,550
Bearer bonds takes on a whole new meaning after this!
我们的债权人松口气了

879
00:58:15,110 --> 00:58:18,150
Talk about a bear market! Hello? Mooners Anonymous.
你说得对    喂？情况怎样

880
00:58:18,230 --> 00:58:21,140
This is Wei Wei from Coopers & Lybrand. Is that Nick?
高柏来班公司的维维             尼克吗

881
00:58:21,230 --> 00:58:22,660
Speaking.
对

882
00:58:22,750 --> 00:58:27,430
I'm compiling the end-of-year audit. There seems to be a big hole in the accounts.
我核对年结时发现有数目不符

883
00:58:27,510 --> 00:58:30,020
I'm missing the 7.78 billion yen...
新加坡股票市场少点我

884
00:58:30,110 --> 00:58:32,100
...receivable from SIMEX.
七十七亿八千万日圆

885
00:58:36,390 --> 00:58:38,460
Nick, can you hear me?
尼克，你听到吗

886
00:58:38,550 --> 00:58:41,020
Is everything all right?
没事吧

887
00:58:41,630 --> 00:58:44,190
It's a little complicated. What do you need?
情况有点复杂，想怎样？

888
00:58:44,270 --> 00:58:46,100
I can't find any paperwork.
我找不到文件

889
00:58:47,510 --> 00:58:51,180
It was an over-the-counter trade between Speer, Leads and Kellagg...
这是嘉诺和伦敦霸菱的交易

890
00:58:51,270 --> 00:58:54,260
...and Barings London. It fell through the computer system.
所以没记在电脑 我和电脑的经理

891
00:58:54,350 --> 00:58:56,460
I'll have a word with the systems manager.
商讨后再找你

892
00:58:56,550 --> 00:58:58,500
I need three bits of paper.
我要三方面文件

893
00:58:58,590 --> 00:59:02,100
One: confirmation from SLK that the 7.78 billion yen will be paid.
第一是嘉诺证明文件  显示支付那七十七亿八千万

894
00:59:02,190 --> 00:59:05,340
Two: sight of your bank balance to show it's been received.
第二是你们的银行结算  显示接收了

895
00:59:05,430 --> 00:59:10,580
And three: a note from Ron Baker saying he's aware of the deal and approves it.
第三是朗伯嘉的证明信  表示他知这交易

896
00:59:13,870 --> 00:59:15,700
Well?
怎样？

897
00:59:15,780 --> 00:59:17,580
Oh, it's just a computer glitch.
没什么，电脑出错

898
00:59:17,660 --> 00:59:20,220
They're doing their annual audit.
他们进行结算

899
01:00:40,900 --> 01:00:45,610
And so, with scissors and paste, I created $78 million out of thin air.
将会支付七十七亿八千万日圆  利用剪贴便创造了

900
01:00:46,900 --> 01:00:49,280
This was forgery, pure and simple,...
伪造过程非常简单

901
01:00:50,180 --> 01:00:52,400
...and there was no going back.
迫我走到不归路

902
01:00:52,490 --> 01:00:54,450
- Nick! - Simon.
尼克

903
01:00:54,530 --> 01:00:56,680
Jesus, you almost gave me a heart attack!
辛逊，你把我吓倒

904
01:00:56,770 --> 01:01:00,610
- What's this missing seven billion yen? - Oh, that's a nightmare.
为何会损失七十亿日圆                  那是个噩梦...

905
01:01:00,690 --> 01:01:03,250
It's an OTC trade that was incorrectly booked.
上月的结算纪录错误

906
01:01:03,330 --> 01:01:05,640
The auditors are really on my case about it.
核数师因这问题找我

907
01:01:05,730 --> 01:01:08,690
It's a pain in the arse, but we've got to get it sorted.
我们要尽快纠正错误

908
01:01:08,770 --> 01:01:11,050
The point is, we're owed the money by SLK.
问题是欠SLK款项

909
01:01:11,130 --> 01:01:12,770
Who the hell are SLK?
谁是SLK？

910
01:01:12,850 --> 01:01:15,730
Speer, Leads and Kellagg. It's a brokerage house.
是嘉诺股票行

911
01:01:15,810 --> 01:01:19,170
Better send me a memo as soon as. Get these auditors off my back.
给我内部报告            要尽快解决

912
01:01:19,250 --> 01:01:21,640
Sure, Simon. Don't worry, I'm onto it.
当然，放心，我会处理

913
01:01:28,370 --> 01:01:31,920
Bonnie, it's Nick. Listen. Listen very carefully.
邦妮，我是尼克       留心听我说

914
01:01:32,010 --> 01:01:37,610
Transfer 7.78 billion yen from the client account to the house account tomorrow.
从客户中取七十七亿八千万日圆  转到公司的户口内

915
01:01:37,690 --> 01:01:39,200
But it won't go!
但资金不足怎进行交易

916
01:01:39,290 --> 01:01:41,090
There isn't enough money.
但资金不足怎进行交易

917
01:01:41,170 --> 01:01:45,560
I know that, but then you can reverse it. It's just an electronic transaction.
我知，但可以立刻转回去

918
01:01:45,650 --> 01:01:48,560
But I want the transfer done. And I want the bank...
只是电子交易  我需要进行

919
01:01:48,650 --> 01:01:53,360
...to send us a fax of the statement, showing the 7.78 billion yen credit.
要在银行月结上  看到这宗交易

920
01:01:55,210 --> 01:01:57,360
All right, Nick. If you say so.
好的，尼克，就这样办

921
01:01:57,450 --> 01:01:59,010
Cheers, Bonnie.
谢谢你

922
01:02:00,810 --> 01:02:02,680
Nick?
尼克

923
01:02:02,770 --> 01:02:04,960
What's all this about seven billion yen?
那七十亿怎么了？

924
01:02:05,050 --> 01:02:08,000
Someone from London, Tony Hawes, was looking for you.
有个叫东尼的人从伦敦来电找你

925
01:02:08,090 --> 01:02:11,640
Jesus Christ, if I hear any more about this seven billion yen...
我不想再听到这七十亿元的事

926
01:02:11,730 --> 01:02:13,840
It's about $70 million, innit?
这是天文数字

927
01:02:13,930 --> 01:02:15,800
What do you reckon? Red or blue?
怎么了？蓝或红

928
01:02:15,890 --> 01:02:18,680
You think I just walked off with $70 million?
以为我盗取这七十亿

929
01:02:18,770 --> 01:02:20,160
I didn't say that.
我没说

930
01:02:20,250 --> 01:02:22,200
It's a computer error.
是电脑出错

931
01:02:22,290 --> 01:02:27,230
You need someone in the back office, I told you. You're not bloomin' Superman!
需要人协助文职工作   说过你不是超人

932
01:02:27,320 --> 01:02:28,960
Don't start all that again.
丽莎，别吵架

933
01:02:29,040 --> 01:02:31,320
It wouldn't have happened if I'd been there.
若我在可以帮助你

934
01:02:31,760 --> 01:02:33,990
Right. I'm goin' out.
对，我出去

935
01:02:34,080 --> 01:02:36,360
- Where are you going? - To get pissed.
去哪里                       去死

936
01:02:36,440 --> 01:02:39,320
If anyone calls, tell 'em I've gone to South America.
有人找我，说我在南美洲

937
01:02:39,400 --> 01:02:41,960
Well, you can bloody stay there, then!
你别回来好了

938
01:02:42,040 --> 01:02:44,030
Twat!
该死的

939
01:03:25,560 --> 01:03:28,200
What have you done now, Leeson?
利森，干什么

940
01:03:28,280 --> 01:03:30,270
What have you done now?
你到底干了什么

941
01:03:42,810 --> 01:03:45,410
（尼克和丽莎启）

942
01:03:48,760 --> 01:03:51,590
Come in.
进来

943
01:03:57,600 --> 01:04:00,550
I thought you'd like to know the audit's been cleared.
核数工作完成了

944
01:04:00,640 --> 01:04:04,510
- Nick sent the papers. Everyone's happy. - Thanks, Ron.
尼克把文件交了   他们很满意    谢谢

945
01:04:04,590 --> 01:04:08,910
Technically we've breached SIMEX rules, but it was just a non-transaction.
技术上是违反    新加坡市场规例

946
01:04:08,990 --> 01:04:10,550
With any luck...
但基本上没有进行过交易

947
01:04:10,630 --> 01:04:15,100
...the auditors won't mention it, or we may have problems with the local regulator.
希望核数师不会提到这点   否则监察机构会找麻烦

948
01:04:15,190 --> 01:04:17,420
Sounds sensible.
言之有理

949
01:04:17,510 --> 01:04:22,510
Do you know, Nick made $10 million doing arbitrage in a week?
知道尼克一周内赚到一千万吗

950
01:04:22,590 --> 01:04:25,350
That's about... half a billion dollars a year.
一年便有五亿

951
01:04:25,430 --> 01:04:27,500
The guy's a turbo arbitrageur!
他是钞票印刷机

952
01:04:27,590 --> 01:04:31,380
If he's doing that amount of business for that amount of profit,...
以他赚钱的速度

953
01:04:31,470 --> 01:04:35,100
...why don't we shut down the rest of the bank? We're just overhead.
为何不索性把银行关掉了  连运作也省却

954
01:04:35,190 --> 01:04:36,750
Yeah!
对

955
01:04:46,750 --> 01:04:48,820
- Hello? - Nick,...
尼克

956
01:04:48,910 --> 01:04:51,740
...are you avoiding me? I've been trying you for days.
你在逃避我吗？找你多天

957
01:04:51,830 --> 01:04:53,630
Sorry, Tony, it's been chaos.
东尼，对不起，我们忙于核数

958
01:04:53,710 --> 01:04:56,100
The audit went through. I thought you knew.
东尼，对不起，我们忙于核数

959
01:04:56,190 --> 01:04:59,180
- It's this SLK thing. - It's all been cleared up.
是SLK的事    已经查清楚

960
01:04:59,870 --> 01:05:04,460
I know. What's bothering me is where you got all the money to actually...
我知道  你如何有钱支付给SLK

961
01:05:04,550 --> 01:05:06,500
...well, pay SLK in the first place.
你如何有钱支付给SLK

962
01:05:06,590 --> 01:05:09,060
I mean, it's the equivalent of $78 million!
总数共七千八百万元呢

963
01:05:09,150 --> 01:05:11,140
It doesn't add up, you know.
这项数目不对

964
01:05:12,350 --> 01:05:17,220
It's obvious. It's part of the funding we've had from you over the past few weeks.
东尼，钱是你数星期批给我们的

965
01:05:17,310 --> 01:05:18,340
Yes.
