对，所以我们有能力还款给你

969
01:05:29,790 --> 01:05:33,060
That'll be good. Er... getting our funding down will be good.
很好   请尽快把钱交给我们

970
01:05:33,150 --> 01:05:35,380
I'm having to juggle quite a few balls.
我还要处理其他问题

971
01:05:35,470 --> 01:05:37,580
We all are, Tony. Look, I've got to dash.
我们也是，东尼，信我

972
01:05:37,670 --> 01:05:39,460
I've got company for dinner.
要挂线了，我要参加公司晚宴

973
01:05:39,540 --> 01:05:42,340
Of course. Thanks, Nick.
尼克，谢谢你把事情交待清楚

974
01:05:42,420 --> 01:05:44,420
Thanks for... clearing that up.
尼克，谢谢你把事情交待清楚

975
01:05:51,020 --> 01:05:52,980
Yes, Ron. What do you want?
朗，你想怎样

976
01:05:53,060 --> 01:05:55,740
It's me, you wanker! Danny.
怎么了，我是丹尼

977
01:05:55,820 --> 01:05:59,340
Bubble? What are you doing calling me in the middle of the night?
是“吹波”  这么晚找我有什么事

978
01:05:59,420 --> 01:06:01,300
Are you anywhere near a TV?
你附近有电视吗

979
01:06:01,380 --> 01:06:03,580
I suggest you tune in to CNN.
快看美国有线新闻

980
01:06:08,460 --> 01:06:11,660
The worst damage was in the seaport of Kobe.
神户海港所受的破坏最严重

981
01:06:11,740 --> 01:06:14,050
Road and rail links are shattered...
道路及铁路糟破坏

982
01:06:14,780 --> 01:06:17,770
Jesus, an earthquake! That's all we fuckin' need.
房屋倒塌，多处起火   该死，是地震

983
01:06:19,180 --> 01:06:21,170
This is gonna kill the market, man.
市场一定受到影响

984
01:06:21,260 --> 01:06:24,090
The Nikkei's gonna fall through the fuckin' floor!
日经指数大幅下泻

985
01:06:24,180 --> 01:06:26,490
...milling around in search of help.
日经指数大幅下泻

986
01:06:26,580 --> 01:06:29,700
Rescue operations are going to be complicated, long...

987
01:06:29,780 --> 01:06:34,460
...and expensive. Mike Chinoy, CNN, reporting live from Tokyo.

988
01:06:57,020 --> 01:07:00,850
Market's down 300 points, you stand there cool as a fuckin' cucumber.
股市下跌三百点，我们有难了

989
01:07:00,940 --> 01:07:03,010
The way I see it, it's an opportunity.
“吹波”  ，我认为是机会

990
01:07:03,100 --> 01:07:07,330
I'm gonna buy into the market. Buy it all the way back up to 19,000.
我要趁低入市  很快股市回升至千九点

991
01:07:12,020 --> 01:07:15,210
Fuckin' true what they say about your gonads, mate.
你的眼光真准

992
01:07:16,250 --> 01:07:18,250
See what I mean?
看到了吧

993
01:07:19,250 --> 01:07:23,850
Think I'll give Fernando a bell in Tokyo, see what's shakin'. No pun intended.
我致东京的法兰度  看情况怎样 应不会摇动

994
01:07:23,930 --> 01:07:26,320
It's Nick. What's the situation in Kobe?
法兰度，神户的情况怎样

995
01:07:26,410 --> 01:07:30,490
We've been trying to contact our friends, but the lines are down.
我们无法联络那里的朋友

996
01:07:30,570 --> 01:07:32,480
Hold it a second. We got movement.
尼克，我们这边有变

997
01:07:32,570 --> 01:07:35,800
Holy shit, selling! There's some selling!
有人大手沽货

998
01:07:36,610 --> 01:07:38,650
Fuckin' hell, it's in free fall!
股市大泻

999
01:07:38,730 --> 01:07:40,720
I've never seen it move so fast.
从没见过市场下跌这么快

1000
01:07:41,850 --> 01:07:44,760
350! 350!
三百五十...

1001
01:07:44,850 --> 01:07:46,170
350!
三百五十...

1002
01:07:57,650 --> 01:07:59,720
Nick?
尼克

1003
01:07:59,810 --> 01:08:01,800
Sure you don't want us to stay?
不要我们留下吗

1004
01:08:03,330 --> 01:08:05,290
No, I... I'm fine. You go.
不，我没事，回去吧

1005
01:08:05,370 --> 01:08:07,440
You'll make it right, Nick.
你会熬过的

1006
01:08:08,050 --> 01:08:09,930
We all believe in you.
我们对你有信心

1007
01:08:43,330 --> 01:08:45,320
50 million!
五千万

1008
01:08:49,040 --> 01:08:50,760
I,...
我...尼克利森

1009
01:08:50,840 --> 01:08:53,150
...Nicholas Leeson,...
我...尼克利森

1010
01:08:53,240 --> 01:08:55,080
...have lost...
在一天内损失了五千万英镑

1011
01:08:55,160 --> 01:08:57,160
...50 million quid...
在一天内损失了五千万英镑

1012
01:08:58,080 --> 01:09:00,070
...in one day!
在一天内损失了五千万英镑

1013
01:09:05,080 --> 01:09:07,040
What does he do, exactly?
他干了什么

1014
01:09:07,120 --> 01:09:09,590
That's what no one seems able to explain.
那边无人向我解释

1015
01:09:09,680 --> 01:09:13,390
It's simple. He switches contracts between Osaka and SIMEX,...
很简单 将大阪和新加坡市场的合约对调

1016
01:09:13,480 --> 01:09:16,760
...exploiting price differentials between the two markets.
看看两个市场的价格差距

1017
01:09:16,840 --> 01:09:19,670
That's how he offers the best deals to our customers.
然后用最好的价钱卖给顾客

1018
01:09:19,760 --> 01:09:22,510
If it's that easy, why isn't everybody doing it?
这么简单为何没有人这样做

1019
01:09:22,600 --> 01:09:27,070
Because he's absolutely in the vortex of the information curve over there.
因他有内幕消息

1020
01:09:27,160 --> 01:09:30,070
He's discovered a whole new way of making money.
发现一项全新的赚钱大计

1021
01:09:30,720 --> 01:09:35,030
Well, he's giving us horrendous funding problems, that's all I know.
我知我们的基金遇到难题

1022
01:09:36,200 --> 01:09:40,270
He doesn't do things by the book, Ron. He just doesn't respect the rules.
他不按规条办事，不遵守规例

1023
01:09:40,360 --> 01:09:44,070
Is he really the kind of person we should be employing at Barings?
霸菱银行要聘请这样的人吗

1024
01:09:44,160 --> 01:09:49,110
Oh, fuck the rules. It's barrow boys like Nick who are turning the City around.
东尼，别管规条 像尼克这小子才能令伦敦反转

1025
01:09:49,200 --> 01:09:53,590
You can't run a modern financial centre with a bunch of Hooray Henries.
但我们不能像他管理现代的财经

1026
01:09:58,320 --> 01:09:59,720
Bastard!
混旦

1027
01:09:59,800 --> 01:10:01,790
Wakey-wakey!
华基    你仍在买卖吗

1028
01:10:02,360 --> 01:10:04,710
- What's the action, mate? - You tell me.
华基    你仍在买卖吗    情况怎样

1029
01:10:04,800 --> 01:10:07,670
The market's up and down like a tart's knickers.
天晓得，市场波幅不定

1030
01:10:07,760 --> 01:10:10,950
- I think the worst is over. - Who knows? You could be right.
我猜最坏的情况已过了    或许是吧

1031
01:10:11,040 --> 01:10:12,990
Well, that's my hunch anyway.
我相信我的想法

1032
01:10:13,080 --> 01:10:15,670
Listen, I was out last night with that Loy.
我昨晚和路透社记者莱外出

1033
01:10:15,760 --> 01:10:17,790
You know, that journo from Reuters.
我昨晚和路透社记者莱外出

1034
01:10:17,880 --> 01:10:20,390
He's convinced there's no mystery customer.
他相信你没有神秘顾客了

1035
01:10:20,480 --> 01:10:24,100
He reckons it's you. He thinks you're trading on your own account.
他们相信那是你 他猜你在没合约下为自己作买卖

1036
01:10:24,200 --> 01:10:26,150
Without the bank's approval.
他猜你在没合约下为自己作买卖

1037
01:10:28,350 --> 01:10:30,470
Now, you're not that crazy, are you?
这不是真的吧    你认为呢

1038
01:10:30,550 --> 01:10:32,430
What do you think?
这不是真的吧    你认为呢

1039
01:10:32,510 --> 01:10:35,790
Who, then? Beaumarchais? I thought he'd given you the elbow.
若是真的，那班老鬼必定杀了你

1040
01:10:35,870 --> 01:10:39,020
- I can't tell you. - Come on. It's me, Danny Boy!
这是秘密  来吧，我是自己人

1041
01:10:39,110 --> 01:10:42,420
I could tell you... but I'd have to shoot you afterwards.
我可告诉你，但之后要杀你灭口

1042
01:10:45,510 --> 01:10:48,190
I know one thing. If Customer X didn't exist,...
若顾客X不存在，你便要创造他

1043
01:10:48,270 --> 01:10:50,310
...you'd have to invent him.
若顾客X不存在，你便要创造他

1044
01:10:52,430 --> 01:10:55,070
45 million? You've already had 100 this week.
四千五百万？本周已调动一亿

1045
01:10:55,150 --> 01:10:59,540
Everybody's had an advance margin call from SIMEX on their client positions.
每位新加坡股市的顾客  接到期指的通知电话

1046
01:10:59,630 --> 01:11:02,830
They're worried about stability with these big movements.
他们担心股市波动会影响市场

1047
01:11:02,910 --> 01:11:04,900
It's an emergency measure?
这是紧急情况吗    对

1048
01:11:06,030 --> 01:11:08,020
Isn't everybody squealing out there?
各人都沽售出货吗

1049
01:11:08,110 --> 01:11:11,100
No, we'll get it back when the market calms down.
待市场转好后会再入货

1050
01:11:12,150 --> 01:11:15,140
Nick, when are you gonna reduce these positions?
尼克，你会沽货吗

1051
01:11:15,230 --> 01:11:17,620
The bean counters are freakin' out!
财经管理公司的会计师很担心

1052
01:11:17,710 --> 01:11:20,140
Ron! Didn't know you were there.
朗，我不知你在这里

1053
01:11:20,230 --> 01:11:23,820
For fuck's sake, we've had the Bank of International Settlements...
我们的客户问霸菱能够支付

1054
01:11:23,910 --> 01:11:26,470
...asking if Barings can meet its margin payments!
I展款项 任何差错都会影响公司形象

1055
01:11:26,550 --> 01:11:30,260
- It is not good for the image! - I hear you, Ron. It's a tight market.
朗，市场竞争激烈

1056
01:11:30,350 --> 01:11:32,540
Yeah, well, you've really gotta try.
所以要尽力而为

1057
01:11:32,630 --> 01:11:34,620
Take a hit on it if you have to.
别让客户损失

1058
01:11:34,710 --> 01:11:38,990
I know Norris is gonna want to discuss it with you when he's out there next week.
罗斯下周会和你商讨这个问题

1059
01:11:39,070 --> 01:11:40,740
Norris?
罗斯

1060
01:11:41,510 --> 01:11:44,460
- I didn't know he was coming. - Yeah, with Tony Hawes.
我不知他来          他和东尼贺斯一起到

1061
01:11:44,550 --> 01:11:48,860
They want to check the numbers. Iron out these funding problems once and for all!
他们要核数找出基金的问题

1062
01:11:54,150 --> 01:11:58,420
There was no way I could reduce my positions without the market collapsing.
我不能在市场不下泻时削减欠款

1063
01:11:58,510 --> 01:12:03,210
By the time they got to Singapore I was in deeper than ever, faxing Brenda daily,...
他们到新加坡时我已泥足深陷

1064
01:12:03,300 --> 01:12:06,060
...30, 40 million dollars at a time.
每次亏损三、四千万元

1065
01:12:07,300 --> 01:12:09,300
They were gonna kill me.
他们不会放过我

1066
01:12:32,020 --> 01:12:34,010
Lookin' like shit, Nick.
你看来糟透了

1067
01:12:35,580 --> 01:12:37,650
Lookin' like fuckin' shit, mate.
你看来糟透了

1068
01:12:45,340 --> 01:12:47,570
- Good evening, sir. - Good evening.
晚安    晚安

1069
01:12:54,060 --> 01:12:57,260
His approach shot sliced into the woods...

1070
01:12:58,340 --> 01:13:01,650
- Nick. There you are. - I'm sorry I'm a little bit late.
尼克，你在这里                对不起，我迟了

1071
01:13:01,740 --> 01:13:04,460
- What'll you have? - A beer would be great, thanks.
很高兴见到你              你喝什么？    啤酒

1072
01:13:04,540 --> 01:13:06,530
Another Tiger, please.
再来老虎啤

1073
01:13:06,980 --> 01:13:08,970
Nick...
尼克

1074
01:13:10,340 --> 01:13:13,610
- How was the market today? - It stayed between 18,000 and 18,300.
今天市场怎样            今在一千八百三十之间上落

1075
01:13:13,700 --> 01:13:15,690
It's settled after the earthquake.
地震发生后已经稳定下来

1076
01:13:15,780 --> 01:13:18,050
Happy with the positions you're running?
你手上的帐户还可以吗

1077
01:13:18,140 --> 01:13:21,530
I'm relaxed. They're March contracts, so I'll let them expire.
它们都是主要客户的合约  可以待它们自动终结

1078
01:13:21,620 --> 01:13:23,330
- Good. - Thanks.
很好     谢谢

1079
01:13:25,180 --> 01:13:28,370
Now, we've had a lot of stick... over funding.
我们有太多投资基金了

1080
01:13:28,460 --> 01:13:32,730
Brenda Granger tells me we're borrowing all over Japan to get the funds to you.
班迪说他们向日本公司...       借资金给你

1081
01:13:32,820 --> 01:13:35,010
People are beginning to talk, Nick.
市场上开始有谣传了

1082
01:13:35,100 --> 01:13:37,210
I understand.
我明白

1083
01:13:37,290 --> 01:13:39,130
I understand completely.
我完全明白

1084
01:13:39,690 --> 01:13:41,290
Excellent.
很好...

1085
01:13:41,370 --> 01:13:43,370
Good man.
很好

1086
01:13:45,170 --> 01:13:49,130
And that was it. That was apparently all he had to say on the subject...
这么简单  他看来好像要揭穿我的秘密

1087
01:13:49,210 --> 01:13:53,810
...of my enormous exposure causing so many ulcers throughout Barings.
这秘密足以令霸菱银行王国倾倒

1088
01:13:53,890 --> 01:13:56,650
Better than you get in London, that's for sure!
比伦敦情况更好

1089
01:13:56,730 --> 01:13:58,610
You'll enjoy the next course.
很快送上下一道菜式

1090
01:13:58,690 --> 01:14:01,680
- Lobster, sir? - No, thanks. I'm not very hungry.
要龙虾吗             没有，我不太肚饿

1091
01:14:01,770 --> 01:14:04,410
I should have been able to relax after that,...
办完事后  我可以好好休息

1092
01:14:04,490 --> 01:14:08,850
...but I couldn't stop thinking about the losses in the five eights account.
但我不停在想那个幸运户口

1093
01:14:08,930 --> 01:14:11,450
Shame you can't stay for the match on Saturday.
真可惜，你不能欣赏周六的比赛

1094
01:14:16,410 --> 01:14:18,400
You're down for 450, aren't you?
你有四百五十万元花红

1095
01:14:20,410 --> 01:14:22,480
Your bonus.
你的偿金？只剩下周时间

1096
01:14:22,570 --> 01:14:24,610
Only a week to go.
你的偿金？只剩下周时间

1097
01:14:26,210 --> 01:14:27,640
Sorry?
什么？

1098
01:14:27,730 --> 01:14:32,250
Have you thought about what you're going to do with it? Only a week to go!
只剩下一周时间给你想

1099
01:14:36,770 --> 01:14:39,760
Ahem! Excuse me. I have an announcement to make.
各位，我有要事宣布

1100
01:14:42,450 --> 01:14:46,360
I know that some of you are worried about our exposure in the market,...
我明白你们担心近期的炒卖活动

1101
01:14:46,450 --> 01:14:51,360
...and you're probably wondering about the identity of our mystery Customer X.
你们也对我们神秘X客户很好奇

1102
01:14:52,170 --> 01:14:54,560
Well, the fact is...
事实上...他并不存在

1103
01:14:54,650 --> 01:14:56,640
...he doesn't exist.
事实上...他并不存在

1104
01:14:57,410 --> 01:14:59,640
We are the customer: Barings.
霸菱就那个神秘客户

1105
01:14:59,730 --> 01:15:02,240
Look properly at the five eights account -
你仔细看看五个八的户口

1106
01:15:02,330 --> 01:15:05,600
...which is not a client account, it's an errors account -
发现那是个错误户口

1107
01:15:05,690 --> 01:15:10,240
...and you'll realise it's concealing losses in the region of 200 million.
用来掩饰亚洲区内  二亿英镑的损失

1108
01:15:10,930 --> 01:15:14,880
No, I tell a lie. It's more like 230 after today!
我说谎  到今天损失不止这个数

1109
01:15:25,840 --> 01:15:28,880
What are you going to do with all that money, Nick?
你怎样用那笔钱

1110
01:15:36,200 --> 01:15:38,720
Well, I won't spend it on futures and options!
我不会用来投资期货和期权

1111
01:15:42,680 --> 01:15:44,640
- That's very good. - Very good.
很好    很好

1112
01:15:51,520 --> 01:15:54,560
I was living from day to day, hoping for a miracle.
我每天都望天打挂  希望奇迹出现

1113
01:15:56,200 --> 01:16:00,080
I wasn't running a position any more. The position was running me.
我不能控制市场，但被市场控制

1114
01:16:01,680 --> 01:16:04,800
Man, look at the state you're in. You got the bloody shakes!
你看来很疲乏，昨晚玩得很晚吗

1115
01:16:04,880 --> 01:16:07,520
- You been on the razz all night? - Nah.
你看来很疲乏，昨晚玩得很晚吗

1116
01:16:07,600 --> 01:16:10,750
- I'm just getting killed by the market. - Tell me about it!
这个股市差点把我害死               为什么

1117
01:16:10,840 --> 01:16:12,830
I've had a shitty week too.
今个星期并不易过

1118
01:16:15,360 --> 01:16:17,350
Penguin? You lucky sod!
你搞什么

1119
01:16:18,120 --> 01:16:20,070
Do you know how rare they are?
你知他们多疯狂吗

1120
01:16:20,160 --> 01:16:22,150
Do you know?
你知他们多疯狂吗

1121
01:16:26,320 --> 01:16:29,390
- It ain't that bloody funny! - Lucky Leeson!
我不是开玩笑    你真够运

1122
01:16:29,480 --> 01:16:32,230
You have it. I'm not laughing at you, Bubble.
“吹波”  ，我不是取笑你

1123
01:16:34,080 --> 01:16:36,070
Fuck! Sorry.
对不起

1124
01:16:37,640 --> 01:16:40,990
'Ey-ey-ey-ey-ey! You really are in a bad way, ain't ya?
你的情况真不妙吗

1125
01:16:41,800 --> 01:16:43,630
What's the matter?
什么事

1126
01:16:46,280 --> 01:16:48,340
I have an unauthorised position.
我干了非法的交易

1127
01:16:52,510 --> 01:16:54,510
Fuckin' hell.
该死，数目多大

1128
01:16:55,510 --> 01:16:56,910
How big?
该死，数目多大

1129
01:16:57,990 --> 01:16:59,980
Big enough to be a problem.
很棘手    真可怜

1130
01:17:01,510 --> 01:17:03,190
Poor bastard!
很棘手    真可怜

1131
01:17:03,270 --> 01:17:06,110
I can't say it comes as a complete surprise.
不过我早料到，

1132
01:17:06,190 --> 01:17:08,420
- Does Lisa know? - No, she'd kill me.
丽莎知吗       不，否则她会杀了我

1133
01:17:09,310 --> 01:17:13,830
She's got enough on her plate. She's just waiting for my bonus so we can go home!
真可怜，这对她是双重打击  她望我能取得花红然后回老家

1134
01:17:13,910 --> 01:17:15,900
So what are you gonna do?
你打算怎样

1135
01:17:17,590 --> 01:17:21,950
Well... I just have to keep buying futures to support the market.
我要继续买期货直至补仓成功

1136
01:17:22,030 --> 01:17:24,910
If it sticks at 18,000, my options are still in the money...
若指数维持在一万八千点

1137
01:17:25,240 --> 01:17:27,110
I could get the position back.
我有期权在手定会取回控制权

1138
01:17:27,270 --> 01:17:29,990
- I may even come out ahead. - Nick...
可能会赚钱

1139
01:17:30,070 --> 01:17:32,030
You listen to me now, right.
听我说...别和市场斗气

1140
01:17:32,110 --> 01:17:34,100
You don't fight the market, man.
听我说...别和市场斗气

1141
01:17:34,190 --> 01:17:38,500
Even if you can make the margin calls, what happens when the contracts expire?
即使你投资I展若合约完结怎办

1142
01:17:38,590 --> 01:17:42,220
The way the market's going, your losses could be catastrophic!
到时你更泥足深陷

1143
01:18:07,390 --> 01:18:10,110
Five for a thousand, five for a thousand! Come on!
一千放五手...

1144
01:18:10,190 --> 01:18:14,260
George, move this fuckin' market! If it stays below 18,000 we're dead!
佐治，快令股市上升 停留一万八千点以下便无法翻身

1145
01:18:42,700 --> 01:18:43,690
Nick.
尼克

1146
01:18:47,620 --> 01:18:51,090
Nick, I really need to go over some of the figures with you.
东尼         尼克，我要和你核对帐目

1147
01:18:51,180 --> 01:18:53,170
Sure, Tony.
可以

1148
01:18:57,100 --> 01:18:58,740
Back in a minute.
很快回来

1149
01:19:02,420 --> 01:19:04,410
Seven for five! Seven for five!
股市急泻，我无能为力...

1150
01:19:11,620 --> 01:19:13,340
I'm sorry. Money!
对不起...

1151
01:20:00,130 --> 01:20:04,050
I'd thrown away countless more millions, and it hadn't made a dent.
再损失金钱但始终未能扭转局面

1152
01:20:04,130 --> 01:20:07,650
I was only one day from bonus day, but the game was up.
还有一天要发花红  但游戏继续，

1153
01:20:09,210 --> 01:20:11,200
I was beaten.
我战败了

1154
01:20:48,530 --> 01:20:51,200
Oh, Nick, you're a bloody fool, aren't you?
尼克，你真笨

1155
01:20:52,570 --> 01:20:57,040
Well, it's not the end of the world. You've got your health, you've got me...
不是世界末日，你有健康有我

1156
01:20:57,130 --> 01:20:59,080
Shame about the bonus.
可惜花红没有了

1157
01:20:59,170 --> 01:21:01,160
Sorry.
对不起

1158
01:21:01,770 --> 01:21:04,120
Slow down. The video shop's on the next left.
把车慢下来，商铺就在邻近的铺位

1159
01:21:04,210 --> 01:21:06,360
- I wanna get our deposit back. - Right.
我要取回按金    好吧

1160
01:21:06,450 --> 01:21:08,600
We're gonna need it, darlin'.
我们要这个

1161
01:21:23,370 --> 01:21:26,360
- Hello? - The positions have got bigger!
尼克，情况越来越不妙

1162
01:21:26,450 --> 01:21:29,800
If they aren't reduced I'm coming out there to sort you out!
若它们还没改善我要对付你

1163
01:21:29,890 --> 01:21:33,000
- You're very faint, Ron. - And what's this rumour I hear?
朗，你真不够运

1164
01:21:33,090 --> 01:21:35,390
There's a rumour that we're the customer.
听到传言说我们就是那个顾客

1165
01:21:35,480 --> 01:21:37,550
Sorry, you're gonna have to speak up.
对不起，你要大声点

1166
01:21:37,640 --> 01:21:39,920
Tell me we're not the customer, Nick.
说我们不是那个顾客吧

1167
01:21:40,000 --> 01:21:43,080
- I'm losing you, Ron. - Nick! Nick, are you there?
这里接收很差             尼克，你还在吗

1168
01:21:43,160 --> 01:21:45,150
Goodbye, Ron.
朗，再见了

1169
01:21:48,320 --> 01:21:51,550
They wouldn't give me the full 200, but I stood my ground and got 180.
我坚持要退回按金       他们只发还180元给我

1170
01:21:51,640 --> 01:21:53,630
Good girl.
干得好

1171
01:21:57,760 --> 01:21:59,350
Nick...!
尼克

1172
01:22:10,290 --> 01:22:13,120
（新加坡机场）

